                "typeId": 1,
                "questionText": "Cho tam giác ABC vuông tại A, đường cao AH <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/e1e1b6d1-98b5-45c4-a465-3377621e2e35.png\"/> Kẻ <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/727f42b0-14a7-4e01-976b-3ff7f87d325c.png\"/> <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/4150722a-4749-427e-9bd8-5d04cfdd37ce.png\"/>\na) Cho <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/cb768209-1aee-4f02-a600-66172f3b599e.png\"/>; <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/139bffd9-6f37-419e-90b2-4000e8abb56b.png\"/> Tính AC.\nb) Chứng minh <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/fb6bc2b2-a286-4e0e-a909-5917d895b110.png\"/>\nc) Chứng minh <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/a21c7393-d224-40f8-bc9a-511232c77051.png\"/>\n",
                "answer": "<img src=\"https://asset.moon.vn/img/chat/large/2026/1/ee026f71-8a1c-427e-ac27-6cc98bd68df6.jpg\" data-filename=\"\" style=\"max-width: 600px; height: auto;\"><br>a) <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/7efc5198-7c27-4708-9594-591d57604c5d.png\"/> vuông tại <i>A</i>, áp dụng định lý Pythagore ta có:\n<br><img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/74ec99b1-74db-4853-9daa-6fa5fc07c135.png\"/>\n<br><img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/65cebcc4-e963-41ef-b0ff-2fa44d122b48.png\"/>\n<br><img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/d4384bf0-e931-49c0-85da-f6a72b3b6033.png\"/>\n<br>b) Xét <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/67029b0c-00fd-4188-b39b-07f316582b26.png\"/> và <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/9a2a64d3-c5e0-4b45-ae67-f4b552efa641.png\"/> có:\n<br><img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/eeb27a05-7238-492a-a9d2-baca05a094a9.png\"/>\n<br><img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/0359fc35-7623-4c05-a150-5dd3c2da2c92.png\"/> chung\n<br>Vậy <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/1c33986d-31f6-4388-a5e6-02e2419d0a14.png\"/> (g.g)\n<br>c) <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/84bf5a63-50c9-432d-a702-0462ecfb8a15.png\"/> suy ra <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/dc4659b5-1a77-44a1-ba5b-1e9201fd742c.png\"/>\n<br>Hay <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/e15c1c57-50ea-4c81-b9f8-3696398744e7.png\"/> (1)\n<br>Chứng minh <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/cde8a309-82dc-4604-876d-63dc80eb1c54.png\"/> (g.g) suy ra <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/116baec7-b783-4c3d-b0f4-36d4a3c4b361.png\"/>\n<br>Hay <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/40b207e8-5180-4ed9-a657-36080c6301d5.png\"/> (2)\n<br>Từ (1) và (2) suy ra <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/492b3559-b893-4949-9290-24c7222a9d16.png\"/>\n",
